(172, 1, '2012-05-12 02:00:08', '2012-05-12 02:00:08', 'Mission Statement: <em>Creation Of Society</em> strives to promote a conscious society by leading by example. As a socially conscious team we produce quality products that reiterate our world perspectives and ideological views, in doing so we are able to inspire young minds to be creative and pursue their passion. We strive to allow ourselves as well as our supporters to think outside the social norms and create a positive society for all.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nVision Statement: To promote and grow our brand via unique clothes and wearable art equipped with social and ideological statements as well as, independent documentaries, speaking engagements and multimedia marketing resources. We believe by becoming the change we want to see in the world we can alter the reality we preside in and create, sustain and promote a conscious society for the future.', 'C.reation O.f S.ociety', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-3', '', '', '2012-05-12 02:00:08', '2012-05-12 02:00:08', '', 2, 'http://creationofsociety.com/wp/?p=172', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
